				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/B%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%90%E1%BA%B1ng-giang/poem-UajoSeGVub6lnzC779a8Hg">Bạch Đằng giang - 白藤江</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-ZzgazbvW_31Yn18OxsV6nA">Tùng Thiện Vương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/Chu-h%C3%A0nh/poem-bir5ZWhYxgQK1DghEFLZ1A">Chu hành - 舟行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-lfkyiRMg6zwt6_eiwas6Yg">Vũ Phạm Khải</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-xa-2/poem-tnuLf7_0F-rmVtElAZgfuQ">Đại xa 2 - 大車 2</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/%C4%90%E1%BB%87-nh%E1%BA%A5t-h%E1%BB%93i-ti%E1%BB%81n-thi/poem-hJuhGn5MIIyXVHLnASOMUQ">Đệ nhất hồi tiền thi - 第一回前詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Hoa/%C4%90i%E1%BA%BFu-c%E1%BB%95-chi%E1%BA%BFn-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-v%C4%83n/poem-BtBqulylnFjLUdtgYQ17iQ">Điếu cổ chiến trường văn - 弔古戰場文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Hoa/author-QPqtGH0DoOgqe6s84Y3CFw">Lý Hoa</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/H%E1%BB%89-v%C4%83n-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-t%E1%BA%B7c-phi%C3%AAn-kh%E1%BA%A5u-t%E1%BB%95ng-tho%C3%A1i-kh%E1%BA%A9u-h%C3%A0o-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-FHE_kB_isecAuVwDcHCkYA">Hỉ văn đạo tặc phiên khấu tổng thoái khẩu hào kỳ 3 - 喜聞盜賊蕃寇總退口號其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Ph%E1%BB%8Dc-nhung-nh%C3%A2n/poem-2NYSpqJiCjEUIB2gsgV6qA">Phọc nhung nhân - 縛戎人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/T%E1%BA%B7ng-nh%C3%A2n-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-AJjkh87oxkOOTvCgwXd6Rw">Tặng nhân kỳ 2 - 贈人其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/author-TXAaCmjdRWIV6MkCYE1psQ">Lỗ Tấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-t%C3%AC-b%E1%BB%99-Ti%C3%AAu-lang-trung-th%E1%BA%ADp-huynh/poem-aB57mSvNVwdnkl12M3H0kw">Tặng tì bộ Tiêu lang trung thập huynh - 贈比部蕭郎中十兄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%C3%ADch-mu%E1%BB%99n/poem-v87xCkkTnTZ7HBIiLG2kfg">Thích muộn - 釋悶</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
